Trinity::

She smiled at him, then scratched her head with her paw,"I don't 
know.  I don't remember hating them before.  I just know that since 
after the ship went down, I didn't like them.  My mom and dad were 
maximals. I don't hate them."  She looked up at him with an 
inquizitive look. "Why?"

to know 
> why do you hate Maximals so much?"  After saying this he stops and 
turns back 
> to flying centaur mode.  He reaches behind him and puts Trinity 
down in front 
> of him.  He looks down and smiles.  Seeing her makes him wonder how 
long it 
> has been since he last smiled.
